TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
You ordered a donut soup.

Waiter, the AN225 has my soup.

Seems to be transporting cargo.

Waiter! There's a Gargantua in my soup!

If you don't want it, I'm sure it'll eat it for you.

Waiter, I have no soup!

Ok! Ready to order?

Waiter! Theres a waiter in my soup!

The waiter is on strike.

Waiter! Salyut 1 is in my soup!

Seems to be the first of its kind.

Waiter! There's soup in my soup!

Sorry. Here, I'll take it out [empties bowl completely]

Waiter, Danny2462 is in my soup!

Sorry, I can't do anything. Jool is making me hostage.

Waiter, there's oxidizer all over my soup!

You wanted your soup cold.

Waiter, there's liquid nitrogen above my soup.

Not for long! (puts soup in microwave and runs from explosion)

Waiter, there's an underscore in my soup!

What are you trying to say, sir?

Waiter, there's a Xannari Ferrows in my soup!

Uhh, shoot yourself in the head? And don't die?

Waiter, there's a locked thread in my soup.

Didn't you buy the key to go with it?

Waiter, there's a lock of hair in my soup.

Hang on, I'll get my keys and unlock it.

Waiter, there's a New Horizons in my Plut- uh, I mean soup

Seems to be making history.

Waiter, there's a Yuri Gargarian in my soup!

Are yurilly sure? Is it making you gar-gag?

Waiter, there is a obscure website in my soup!

Seems to be quite disturbing....are you in the deep part of the internet?

Waiter! There's a Kaboom! in my soup!

replace it by a penguinsmeep much better ; )

waiter there's a stars/planets/blackholes ratio in my soup

Seems to be collapsing under infinite density

Waiter! There's a Jebediah in my soup

How careless of me! Here's the "terminate flight" button. ^^

Way tore, dares a flyin mice hoop!

Sorry, can you please speak English?

Waiter, there's a paper in my soup... It says, "FNAF IS EVIL" on it.... I agree.

Well me too, but the fanboys are worse than the game.

Waiter, theres a Missigno in my soup

Oh, really? What's one of those? Er... I mean, yes, it's supposed to be there. Didn't you order the cream of carrot and missigno soup?

Waiter, Schrodinger's cat is in my soup.

I'll take it away if you are allergic to cats, BUT NO REFUNDS (I'm allergic)

Waiter! There is a Booster in my soup!

I'll launch that booster for you

Waiter!!! There's Rocket Fuel in my soup!
